BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Mercury conjunction Saturn
DESCRIPTION:Transit Mercury (Gemini 29°22’) - conjunction - Natal Saturn \nYour ability to concentrate is at its maximum. You are more able to perceive the details and avoid procrastination. Therefore, you may search for peaceful and quiet places where you can think. You will be more negative than usual, especially about your expectations of people. However, you may get good news or advice that will help you. Therefore, try to be optimistic. In exceptional cases, this transit may mean that you will have to say goodbye to someone who is leaving for a long time (for example moving abroad). \n \nTransit Mercury in Natal 9th house: \nNow is one of the best times for studying and career development. If you want to enrol in a university or start looking for a new job, do it now!  \nNow you are a great storyteller and other people will love listening to your stories. You can fully use your creativity when writing, learning and communicating with people, especially those from university environment and from other cultures. Now you can also learn new languages with ease. Overall, you will be tolerant of alternative views, ideas and thoughts. It is also possible that you will get a great new idea that will bring you success.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260601T030900Z
DTEND:20260601T030900Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165727Z
UID:1_tr_me_co_sa
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Mercury trine Venus
DESCRIPTION:Transit Mercury (Cancer 4°24’) - trine - Natal Venus \nYou can easily meet new acquaintances and establish new relationships. Existing relationships, especially romantic relationships, can reach a new level or resolve their issues. This transit is favourable period for negotiating, presenting your thoughts and ideas, public relations and business meetings. You will do very well in these areas because you will be very charming and diplomatic. You can also expect good news.  \n \nTransit Mercury in Natal 9th house: \nNow is one of the best times for studying and career development. If you want to enrol in a university or start looking for a new job, do it now!  \nNow you are a great storyteller and other people will love listening to your stories. You can fully use your creativity when writing, learning and communicating with people, especially those from university environment and from other cultures. Now you can also learn new languages with ease. Overall, you will be tolerant of alternative views, ideas and thoughts. It is also possible that you will get a great new idea that will bring you success.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260604T045000Z
DTEND:20260604T045000Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165727Z
UID:2_tr_me_tr_ve
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Mercury square Pluto
DESCRIPTION:Transit Mercury (Cancer 5°03’) - square - Natal Pluto \nOthers will try to lure you to their side by giving you arguments and showing you their power. Be wary of new ideas and people. Or, on the contrary, you will try to convince someone else of your truth. You may also be fascinated with one thought that you will not be able to release from your head. Therefore, be careful not to develop an obsession with it. This transit is favourable for any research and search activity.  \n \nTransit Mercury in Natal 9th house: \nNow is one of the best times for studying and career development. If you want to enrol in a university or start looking for a new job, do it now!  \nNow you are a great storyteller and other people will love listening to your stories. You can fully use your creativity when writing, learning and communicating with people, especially those from university environment and from other cultures. Now you can also learn new languages with ease. Overall, you will be tolerant of alternative views, ideas and thoughts. It is also possible that you will get a great new idea that will bring you success.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260604T144100Z
DTEND:20260604T144100Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165727Z
UID:3_tr_me_sq_pl
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Venus square Sun
DESCRIPTION:Transit Venus (Cancer 20°41’) - square - Natal Sun \nYou will lack discipline and motivation to work, and you will just want to enjoy life and all it has to offer. Beware of overeating, overspending and avoid any activities that you do not feel comfortable doing. This transit will bring you experiences that you will later remember with a smile. Sometimes it is time to forget about everyday duties and just enjoy your life. \n \nTransit Venus in Natal 10th house: \nThis transit is especially beneficial for your career. You may meet someone who will help you professionally - recommending you to a new position, introducing you to important people or who will give new direction to your career. Your colleagues will like you and respect you. Do not be afraid to use this social influence for career advancement. You can also fall in love with someone you perceive as an authority or someone who is significantly older. However, make sure this romantic relationship is socially acceptable. Focus on building relationships with those who can help you professionally.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260605T115100Z
DTEND:20260605T115100Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165727Z
