DESCRIPTION:Transit Sun (Gemini 28°55’) - square - Natal Mercury \nYou will have plenty of opportunities to communicate your ideas to others. However, avoid being arrogant when you communicate, it could lead to uncomfortable quarrels and misunderstandings. You will also be very busy organising work-related stuff and dealing with authorities.  \n \nTransit Sun in Natal 9th house: \nIt’s time to expand your horizons! This transit usually brings new discoveries.  \nYou may have the urge to seek the meaning of life and you will be open to alternative views. It is a good time to travel longer distances and get to know different cultures. If you are not traveling anywhere, you can expect more interactions with people from other countries or different backgrounds. There may be problems with your father.  \nIt is also an ideal time for education, especially in the field of philosophy, where you will be more interested in various religious movements. If you already belong to a religion, more intensive engagement is expected - for example, you can go to church more often, engage in church activities, etc. During this period, you will also listen more to your guts and intuition. At the same time, you will not be afraid to discuss these topics with others because this transit supports sincerity. But be careful not to be rude and intolerant.  \n \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
