BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Pluto trine Pluto
DESCRIPTION:Transit Pluto (Aquarius 5°03’) - trine - Natal Pluto \nYou will feel the desire to change something for the better. It will concern the spheres of life connected with the houses where the aspect is happening. Stop using old things and approaches that don’t work for you and create something new. These can be people, things, problems, or thought patterns.  \n \nTransit Pluto in Natal 4th house: \nThis transit will force you to deal with deep-rooted family problems and solve them. The need to fix things at home can also be felt at a physical level, you may for example decide you need to remodel or redecorate your home. You may also try to understand and explore your family history. There is a possibility of moving. \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
