BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Venus trine Moon
DESCRIPTION:Transit Venus (Leo 10°13’) - trine - Natal Moon \nPeople will accept and respect you more. You should therefore use this transit to improve your personal relationships. Other people may ask you for emotional or material support. During this transit you should remember to also do something for yourself. It is the perfect time for beauty treatments, decorating your home, and changing your image. You will be rather passive at work. However, sometimes there is no harm in slowing down and pampering yourself.  \n \nTransit Venus in Natal 10th house: \nThis transit is especially beneficial for your career. You may meet someone who will help you professionally - recommending you to a new position, introducing you to important people or who will give new direction to your career. Your colleagues will like you and respect you. Do not be afraid to use this social influence for career advancement. You can also fall in love with someone you perceive as an authority or someone who is significantly older. However, make sure this romantic relationship is socially acceptable. Focus on building relationships with those who can help you professionally.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
