SUMMARY:Tr. Mercury square Uranus
DESCRIPTION:Transit Mercury (Cancer 25°58’) - square - Natal Uranus \nDuring this transit, you will not be able to slow down your thinking processes. You will tend to treat others with sarcasm and impatience. You will also be frustrated with your daily routine and monotonous activities. Therefore, you will tend not to complete tasks that were assigned to you. Your ideas will not meet with much understanding, which will contribute to your restlessness.  \n \nTransit Mercury in Natal 10th house: \nThis transit will force you to think about your future career path.  \nIt is very likely that you will want to talk to your supervisor about promotion, new responsibilities or plans for the future. If you do business, it is the ideal time to decide on strategies that will help you accomplish your professional goals.  \nYou will think about how your actions will affect the achievement of your goals in the long run. The details will not be very interesting for you because you will be focusing on broader context. It is also a great time to continue your professional training, you may for example decide to attend a course or a training programme. You will get along well with your colleagues during this transit, and you can help each other in professional development. This transit will be particularly beneficial for you if you work with technologies or engage in any form of communication. \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
