BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Mars sextile Mercury
DESCRIPTION:Transit Mars (Taurus 28°55’) - sextile - Natal Mercury \nYour mind is working at full speed and you can approach things with clarity and logic. Use this transit to make important decisions and to plan future activities. If you are traveling somewhere, there will be no obstacles. \n \nTransit Mars in Natal 8th house: \nThis transit will awaken the urge to change in you. If there is something in your life that you are not satisfied with in the long term, you will feel motivated to fundamentally change it. You will do this with the feeling of urgency. At work and in your personal life you will want everything right away and you will tend to be impatient. Be humble and make sure that your ego does not hinder your blooming relationships. If you make a living by trading, your business will flourish. \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
